GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/posts/invalid-id-format
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Post Not Found
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/posts/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Create Post Without Required Fields
# Should return 400 Bad Request
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Test post"
}


### Test: Update Non-Existent Post
PATCH {{apiBaseUrl}}/posts/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This should fail"
}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
# Should return 401 without auth token
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/posts
